            "id": "4580467",
            "title": "Applied Industrial Technologies GAAP EPS of $2.65 beats by $0.01, revenue of $1.25B beats by $20M",
            "description": "<html><body><ul>\n<li>Applied Industrial Technologies <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/20489693-applied-industrial-technologies-reports-fiscal-2026-third-quarter-results\">press release</a> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AIT\" title=\"Applied Industrial Technologies, Inc.\">AIT</a></span>): Q3 GAAP EPS of $2.65 <span> beats by $0.01</span>.</li>\n<li>Revenue of $1.25B (+6.8% Y/Y) <span> beats by $20M</span>.</li>\n<li>\n<p data-eci=\"true\">Guidance for our fiscal 2026 year ending June 30, 2026 is updated as follows:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>EPS: $10.64 to $10.75 (prior $10.45 to $10.75) vs $10.66 consensus</li>\n<li>Total sales growth: 7.2% to 7.7% (prior 5.5% to 7.0%)</li>\n<li>Organic sales growth: 3.8% to 4.2% (prior 2.5% to 4.0%)</li>\n<li>EBITDA margin: 12.3% to 12.4% (prior 12.2% to 12.4%)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Updated guidance assumes the following for our fiscal fourth quarter ending June 30, 2026:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>EPS: $2.85 to $2.96</li>\n<li>Total sales growth: 4.5% to 6.0%</li>\n<li>Organic sales growth: 4.0% to 5.5% year over year</li>\n<li>EBITDA margin: 12.6% to 12.8%</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"signup_widget_placeholder\"></div>\n</body></html>",
